node.text:
The people who cheat…
.
Don’t just cheat on spouses…
.
They cheat on their health…
.
They cheat on their work…
.
They cheat on their goals…
.
They cheat on THEMSELVES.
.
We’ve all made mistakes.
.
We’ve all been there.
.
But once you know, there’s no more excuses.
.
The same mistake twice is a DECISION.
.
#choices

They're lying.
